text: Nicholle Tom (born 23 March, 1978) is an American television program and movie actress. She played Maggie Sheffield in the sitcom The Nanny (1993 to 1999) and Ryce Newton in the Beethoven movies and related TV show. Her sister, Heather Tom, is also an actress. Nicholle Tom was born in Hinsdale, Illinois. ==Reference== ==Other websites== * Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Illinois Category:1978 births Category:Living people
